2.88 2026-04-03

  Bug Fixes:
  - Fix razorhome option assignment and readlink safety in
    Config.pm. (PR #36)
  - Prevent argument mutation and data loss in SIS parsing
    functions. (PR #42)
  - Fix bugs in preprocessing and engine modules. (PR #41)
  - Replace two-arg open with three-arg form in Agent.pm. (PR #40)
  - Correct dependency declarations in Makefile.PL and cpanfile.
    (PR #39)
  - Eliminate uninitialized value warnings in Ephemeral.pm. (PR #37)
  - Security hardening: remove unsafe eval, fix file locking, harden
    error handling. (PR #27)

  Improvements:
  - Modernize Perl idioms: three-arg open, lexical filehandles,
    use parent. (PR #24)
  - Add use strict and use warnings to all modules. (PR #25)
  - Remove unused imports, modernize Exporter, simplify Digest::SHA
    fallback. (PR #28)
