  - Fix builds with parallel make at manifypods-razor. (PR #10)

  Improvements:
  - Allow logfile config to use 'stdout' and 'stderr' keywords for
    direct output. (GH #14, PR #15)
  - Use Digest::SHA instead of Digest::SHA1, removing the non-core
    Digest::SHA1 dependency. (PR #11)

